We are Disturbz, baby.

DISTURBZ é o duo idealizado por Renan Guzzi e Willian Puluceno, surgiu no final de 2018 trazendo produções com notáveis meclas de sonoridades que partem do Tech House ao Nu Disco.

Os dois se conhecem desde a infância, quando ainda adolescentes criaram uma banda de Rock n’ Roll. Willian Puluceno continuou sua carreira como músico, sendo baterista e compositor. Renan Guzzi seguiu por outro caminho, foi morar em Londres por cinco anos, onde lá estudou produção musical, tornando-se DJ e produtor, tocando em diversos clubes, como Vaxhall Roof Top and Brixton.

Em 2018, com o retorno de Renan Guzzi ao Brasil, os caminhos opostos que se cruzaram novamente parar criar o Duo. O projeto vem chamando atenção dos apreciadores de música eletrônica em todas as pistas por onde passam.

أعلم أن الحفاظ على الحافز أمامك طوال الوقت أمر صعب، ولن أخبرك أنك ستبقى طوال الوقت على نفس الدرجة من التحفيز، لكن يمكنني أن أساعدك في أن تبقى متحفزًا ومحافظًا على شغفك لأكبر وقتٍ ممكن، فقط اقرأ السطور القادمة ..

ضع هدفًا
كي تبقى متحفزًا يجب أن يكون لديك هدف، حتى ولو كان هدفا صغيرا كأن تشتري قطعة ملابس تعجبك أو تغير هاتفك الجوال، حدد هدفك مهما كان وضعه أمامك، حدد الإطار الزمني، ولكن تذكر أن هدفك يجب أن يكون واقعيا ويمكن تحقيقه.

title: CatchCook.com Video Competition
description:
CatchCook.com is a movement that promotes and rewards a primitive lifestyle where we take responsibility for what we put into our bodies, over unhealthy and unconscious consumerism. Most people believe that food comes from the supermarket, and this platform will aim to change that behaviour by creating and sharing hunting, fishing, spearfishing, farming and gathering videos that promote and motivate a lifestyle free of processed foods, containing growth hormones, pesticides, antibiotics, chemicals and GMOs.

We are so passionate about moving towards a hunting and gathering way-of-life that we are invested in incentivising other like-minded people who are living closer to the earth. CatchCook.com invites anyone who lives a hunter-gather lifestyle anywhere in the world to submit videos of their adventures - whether it’s spearfishing, mushroom foraging or hunting - and you could WIN massive prizes! You want to be a part of this movement…to be a Primal Provider.

Visit: www.catchcook.com

title: Amakha Renda Extra
description:
Oi tudo bem? Eu sou Eleilson Ramos estudante de Publicidade e Propaganda e Webdesign nas horas vagas, mas que não consegui trabalhar com um salário digno na área que tanto me dediquei aos estudos, mas descobri uma maneira de superar todas as dificuldades financeiras com as oportunidades que a Amakha Paris me ofereceu

Após anos trabalhando em empresas no regime CLT descobri como Afiliado da Hotmart a melhor forma de ter renda trabalhando no conforto da minha humilde casa, isso mesmo o tão sonhado “dinheiro online” existe, e o melhor é trabalhar ao lado da minha família, otimizando meu tempo e tendo o que muitas pessoas procuram no mundo atual que é a LIBERDADE.

Com isso consegui superar a crise financeira que estava ao meu redor na falta de emprego e até mesmo nos baixos salários que o mercado oferece.

No início de 2018 eu tive o prazer de descobrir este mundo fantástico de negócios e hoje vivo e dependo apenas de meus esforços na minha casa com meu computador ligado a internet.

title: Kenny Wade - Topic
description: Born in San Antonio - raised in New York - now back in San Antonio. Kenny Wade's music is a mix of East Coast and Down South Funk. He began his career as a battle rapper winning several competitions, then moved on to writing and producing his own beats and music. Kenny Wade founded and ran Royal Coach Records, doing his own marketing and promotion for over 10 years. He is the originator of the 210 anthem that was made for and performed at Sugar's in San Antonio. Kenny Wade is the grandson of a very well known record store owner and local celebrity who went by the name Melvin The Mack. The name of the record store was Music World records, which is the same name that Beyonce's dad uses for his record label today. After his grandad was incarcerated for shooting 2 racists, Kenny Wade was left homeless and made his way through group homes and foster care until he was finally placed in a home. At the age of 18 he found himself homeless again and without any assistance from his social worker he did what he had to do to survive. Now settled back in San Antonio he has secured a nice life situation and is now adjusting his music to match his current life, but he promises to continue to perform his original music because he feels that is still apart of who he is.

title: Overlook Valley Homestead
description:
Hello, thanks for visiting our channel!

Our names are Mark and Sara, we are a simple country family trying to live a healthy and self-sufficient lifestyle . We live on a 27 acre farm in southern Tennessee owned mostly by our parents.We have cows, goats, chickens and 2 dogs

We currently are milking a family cow, gardening, and in the progress of building our barn. We just finished building our greenhouse, in which we start and grow vegetables and some flowers, mostly for our own use as of right now, but we hope to expand that to have some to sell at the farmers mkt.

This channel is about our journey to implement our own homestead, and to help others learn from our experiences.

We invite you to follow us as we grow our homestead!

title: El Mago Carracuclás
description:
El mago Carracuclás, era el mago de los libros, estaba muy triste porque los niños, habían dejado de leer, él lo sabía porque cada vez, que un niño leía un libro, se encendía una lucecita en su castillo y hacía mucho tiempo que no se encendía ninguna.

-¿Qué pasará? A mi amiga el hada de los cuentos tengo que llamar ella me lo dirá.

Y llamó al hada Celeste, El hada fue enseguida al castillo de su amigo, el mago Carracuclás la estaba esperando.

-Pasa querida amiga, me alegro mucho de verte te he llamado para preguntarte si sabes ¿por qué los niños han dejado de leer?

-Sí que lo sé, el Brujo Malacabrú es un brujo muy malvado que odia los cuentos, muchas veces ha intentado destruirlos, pero nunca lo lograba porque yo no lo dejaba, un día muy enfadado vino hacia mi y me dijo:

-Por tu culpa los niños siguen leyendo cuentos, y la magia y la fantasía sigue con ellos pero será por poco tiempo, mi magia hará que no vuelvan a leer más.

My name is Joyce Ann Washington and I’m a 22 year old in my last year of college. I’m majoring in Psychology and minoring in sociology. I have been taking this positivity journey for about 4 years now. I  am a way happier person and I want to share my experience and  journey. I have also been challenging myself to step out of my comfort zone and be the best version of myself. My ultimate goal is to start my own non-profit business for high school and college students. It will be an outreach program to help students get the skills and support they need in order to be successful in college and post-graduation. 

I want to create a brand that promotes positivity, success and happiness.

I am also a self- published author. My book " Dream, Believe, Work Hard, Be Happy," is on Amazon and Kindle today!

Starting today, I will be documenting my road to success on my blog website, https://opengatestoanewworldblog.wordpress.com/. Please check that out as well!

description:
本频道主要分享天下奇事，趣事，新鲜事。每天一个故事，每晚一段传奇

。讲述探究扑朔迷离的悬案，揭开匪夷所思的真相，慨叹曲折离奇的命运

，讲义妙趣横生的传说结合时下民生关注热点，讲述古今中外历史上曾经

发生过的动人故事。不仅仅在于讲一个好听的故事，而是勾连时下热点阐

述观点或道理。使观众在饱耳福，长知识后，对故事本身意义也有所收获

，主题涉及社会生活的方方面面，既有专业的科学知识，以讲故事的形式

同时告诉观众一个科学原理，同时又有生活中遇到的难以解决的问题和不

同寻常的现象，还有自然环境和地理形势的科学探索，包含面比较广泛。

各位小伙伴们觉得有道理就琢磨琢磨，没道理就图一乐，不落俗套，不那

么沉重，目的就是让大家放松，增添点生活情趣。

The main goal of this channel is to document my skateboarding progression, to have fun with my viewers, and more importantly to help other beginner skateboarders, (even advanced skaters) out there who are trying to learn new tricks. Thus, regardless if you are a professional skater, beginner skateboarder, or don't skate at all, I welcome you to the channel! I encourage you to subscribe so you don't miss out on any future uploads! I upload EVERY Friday and sometimes will make a special Saturday bouns video, so make sure those post notifications are on!
